  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>If a creature has cover, but more than half the creature is visible, its cover bonus is reduced to a +2 to AC and a +1 bonus on Reflex saving throws. This partial cover is subject to the GM&lsquo;s discretion.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Partial Cover and Attacks of Opportunity</strong></p>\n<p>You can&rsquo;t execute an attack of opportunity against an opponent with partial cover relative to you.</p>\n<div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Partial Cover and Stealth Checks</strong></p>\n<p>You can cannot use partial cover to make a Stealth check.</p>\n</div>",
